Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.23,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4\fn华文中宋\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0\blur0\c&HF3F9FC&\4c&H000000&\fad(550,550)\alpha20\pos(151.286,238.844)}改編自真實故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4\fn华文中宋\fs18\b0\bord0\shad2\blur1\c&HF3F9FC&\4c&H000000&\fad(550,550)\alpha20\pos(151.286,238.844)}改編自真實故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你得搬出去  圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前外邊很多人認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在肯定還有人記得你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  小杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想聽沃德·艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛打俄羅斯人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那故事我都聽了一百多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一半胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕  他們把這片地賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不離開那椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會和房子一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會落到廢墟里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰克  沃德·艾倫在理發椅上睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在那之前  他立下了規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說  絕對不能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動他的胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點打死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧得三名俄羅斯人撲了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄國大使對沃德說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你要是再敢回俄國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會親自把你押到沙皇面前"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐐銬加身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那些容易變質的  最好先吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴布斯豌豆和羽衣甘藍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必事事操心  小杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在寫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一些圣誕曾經給我講過的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克  我跟姑娘們聊過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不認為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些姑娘們為何不自己開家小俱樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.11,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* You gotta spread joy *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.91,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Up to the maximum *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:21.88,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Bring gloom *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.54,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Down to the minimum *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.88,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Have faith *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.58,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Or pandemonium's *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.58,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Liable to walk up on the scene *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:35.22,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* You got to ac-cent-tchu-ate the positive *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:38.79,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Eliminate the negative *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:42.66,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* And latch on to the affirmative *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:45.47,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Don't mess with Mister In-Between *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:51.67,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* No, don't mess with Mister In-Between *
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:07:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  能給我相機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有沒有給你講過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德·艾倫差點殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就為了他的胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-沒有  -沒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德·艾倫的胡子  是他驕傲與快樂的源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在一次決斗中開槍打了別人  被他父親送去了俄國
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在那之前  他立下了規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說  絕對不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動他的胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點打死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧得三名俄羅斯人撲了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕·穆特里比世上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一個人都更了解沃德·艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一個生來是莊園主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而另一個是奴隸出身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們卻成了性情相投的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:08:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小  我就和圣誕一起打獵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河面上忙碌了一天后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕會坐在壁爐前的搖椅上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凝視著沃德的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我們講故事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著我們漸漸長大  這些故事成了傳奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡管我們之中沒人認識他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻無一例外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都想要成為沃德·艾倫那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你說過要戴手套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴著手套我沒法干活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕  這個觀點毫無道理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德先生  我的手太冷  拉不動它們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴手套也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就撒泡尿在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不撒在你自己手上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手既不冷也不疼  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮到這樣  我就免做不體面的事兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總是免做體面的事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"不體面"  "不"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的說話聲快把鳥兒都驚飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這四條腿的狗可比大多數
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在薩凡納的兩條腿的人懂禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們世世代代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在縣里的河流田野間打獵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,技藝代代相傳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果歷史是我們的宗教信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么打獵就是其中的一件圣事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德·艾倫曾經寫道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:10:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"這條河屬于我們  我們來了"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像無人付出  大教堂便無法建成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這樣的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從未如此近距離面對上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了我這一代  這種傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為了一種生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對最優秀的獵人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是謀生之道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給薩凡納的集市提供新鮮的飛禽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在從事這項買賣的人里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德和圣誕是最出色的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天  圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會打到你自己那份兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我就打了這些鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很樂意只管自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的扔給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我怎么看出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些眼里流露出驚訝的鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是被你打到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們不敢相信這一刻終于到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在鴨子的眼里我可沒看出一絲驚訝  沃德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  你沒看到  所以證明我說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只看到一堆死鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去他們像是笑死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑你足足開了七槍才打死它們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕  你頂著這種名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不應該說出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么諷刺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留著你的花言巧語去跟法官說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德·艾倫的河和生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本該永遠這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是歲月變了  法律也變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而新法律與沃德不共戴天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年輕人怎能為陳腐的法令所羈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N出自莎士比亚《空爱一场》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能反抗生命的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要忘記誓言  找尋自我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則我們會因為守誓而失去本心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人難忘  艾倫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,措辭  精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是生來注定要狩獵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是生來注定要犯法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的確想起某些人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說你在這兩件事上  頗具天賦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讀書慢  法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我真的觸犯了某條法律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我還沒讀到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是狩獵技術高超
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而有人試圖以此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誹謗我的人格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我平時多半盡力隱忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這種個人糾紛居然要訴之公堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能說  我以名譽起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的同伴和我都不想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會觸犯一條真正的法律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者一條錯誤的法律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰能裁定法律是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您可以試試  先生  毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您樂意  會有更多"某些人"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說您在這件事上  頗具天賦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶  救救我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肅靜  請肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你指望我相信你這些說辭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名譽便是我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二者寓于一體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪去我的榮譽  我的生命也就不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《理查三世》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《理查二世》  第一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受指正
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡管如此  你仍然有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但鑒于各方面因素
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緩刑六個月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這段時期內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必須潔身自好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您  法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次  自由征服了司法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N出自莎士比亚《一报还一报》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們本該讓我們留下配額內的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警長今晚能吃頓大餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這根本沒道理   圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們指望我們把鴨子放走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓它們飛到南美洲被別人獵殺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德先生  這只可不會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來  石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三點一刻把船停在寬闊的河段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只當晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝晚上愉快  沃德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不算擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.85,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* I'm a Yankee Doodle, why? *
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.99,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* I report back to Uncle Sam *
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:04.89,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* So I can't shoot birds out the sky *
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你能打得跟我一樣多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你扔掉那雙惡心的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我數了36只
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,訂單是39只
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們打了39只
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我再數一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  姑且算我們獵得一樣多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這絕無可能的抽象現實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留到以后再解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只管帶著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搞定你的鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六十一塊五
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請原諒  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望他沒有打擾你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  他很討人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:18:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老樣子  他離不開我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據管理人員的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的  他不該在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這雙靴子也不該在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這雙靴子  少了幾分個性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但很跟腳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西  準備走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在輪到我被叫"跟著"了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫先生  你的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  你是沃德·艾倫先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們見過面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久仰你的大名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如雷貫耳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多是傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你不是這條河上最好的向導
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不是向導
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打獵為生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  你是獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛好有位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位來自弗吉尼亞州的紳士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是斯圖爾特·格雷厄姆爵士的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們親密的朋友和同僚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想在河上打獵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便誰都可以帶他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要隨便誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要最好的跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說你是最好的  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做一天的向導
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說損失重大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錢不是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是誰都不許碰我的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好極了  那我們就這么說定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很理解你的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證  格雷厄姆先生裝備精良
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個箱子是弗吉尼亞州長送我的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真該好好抱著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你們在弗吉尼亞是怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在這  我們從來不敲鑼打鼓去打獵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經在印度和非洲打過獵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我的副手一直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是來打獵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是來向我的狗秀出身的  格雷厄姆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我的消息沒錯  我確定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人有點矛盾  艾倫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是出國讀過書的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是我的母校牛津大學的高材生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家喻戶曉的"野牛比爾"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N美国陆军侦察兵  曾在八个月内猎杀近五千头野牛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟是艾倫莊園的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一介布衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠自己的雙手討生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與世無爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清心寡欲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂堂莊園主出身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然找個黑鬼做副手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪斯塔布斯先生要大老遠跑去弗吉尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物色良婿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向斯塔布斯小姐承諾過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要給她打只新鮮的野味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得保證我履行我的諾言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得提醒你  你只是個拿錢辦事的向導
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好獵人舉了槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定彈無虛發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會有好下場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕斯塔布斯先生要找你麻煩嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:22:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是有個表親在斯塔布斯家做廚子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她從來不跟我談起她與她無關的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你對斯塔布斯家的小姐一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把萊納家小伙兒迷得顛三倒四那妞么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你表親絕對沒跟你說過這事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呦喂  居然自己尋著路回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  悠著點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好  治安官先生  斯塔布斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們說好了  艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說要帶一位紳士到河上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而  格雷厄姆先生根本不是什么紳士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恐怕他羞辱了您
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和您可愛的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他大放闕詞說他一心覬覦令愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我毅然決然拒絕帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不能用您的錢助紂為虐  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能借一步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我的判斷沒錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全可以避免
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入如此尷尬的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.81,0:23:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿聞其詳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您如果想要野鴨  只管開口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的廚子正愁沒鴨子下鍋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一早給您送去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘎  嘎  嘎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么風把你吹來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答應給令尊送新鮮的野鴨來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出你很守信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還帶了你的小伙伴來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它好像挺高興見到我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樣子雖呆  腦子聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保不齊它還會引用莎士比亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.15,0:24:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請轉告令尊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.32,0:24:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把子彈從鴨子身體里取出來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.59,0:24:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者告訴廚師  隨便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日安  斯塔布斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.60,0:24:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫先生  我想邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.24,0:24:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守信之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.37,0:24:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.97,0:24:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我此前還猶豫是否應該讓艾倫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.08,0:24:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做我們的向導
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.45,0:24:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫先生  我還從來沒在河上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.45,0:24:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細欣賞過這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.92,0:24:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說景色非常美
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.45,0:24:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親可不是劃船高手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.46,0:24:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西  艾倫先生忙于事業  時間金貴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.06,0:24:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  沃德  謝謝你的鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.96,0:25:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敢肯定這會是相當美味的一餐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.80,0:25:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得為表感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.10,0:25:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們至少應該邀請艾倫先生共進晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.00,0:25:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周日吧  德索托
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.00,0:25:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午見
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.07,0:25:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.61,0:25:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏拉圖曾經把人的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比喻成鳥兒的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.59,0:25:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而鳥兒則是浩瀚無垠的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.82,0:25:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發覺知識真是令人琢磨不透
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.53,0:25:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不論邏輯是多么的嚴密
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.56,0:25:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是會有特例出現
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.40,0:25:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.30,0:25:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一只孤雁
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.13,0:25:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開雁群  獨自踏上冒險之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.27,0:25:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是鳥也有理性
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.54,0:25:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊隨渴望的理性是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.75,0:25:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  跟我說說  艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.39,0:26:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明是出國留學的高材生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.45,0:26:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么會自甘選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.56,0:26:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚴酷的野外生活
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.86,0:26:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么要選擇壓抑閉塞的辦公室生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.37,0:26:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不用擔心刮風下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.10,0:26:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人心的風雨比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.04,0:26:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得自然界的風雨更易掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.41,0:26:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加  坦城
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.74,0:26:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.08,0:26:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有幾分道理
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.15,0:26:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  你畢竟還是有著
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.82,0:26:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演講和辯論的天賦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.99,0:26:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有幸曾在法庭上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.29,0:26:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一睹你的風采
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.76,0:26:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我年輕時  曾浪費大好時光
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.03,0:26:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在枯燥的律師辦公室工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.36,0:26:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是我父母的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.16,0:26:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一心想要我干這一行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.70,0:26:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追隨約翰·艾略特·沃德光輝的腳步是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.70,0:26:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎從他那里繼承了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.71,0:26:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫圣誕·穆特里的好黑奴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.21,0:27:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叔叔認為圣誕是極好的向導
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.99,0:27:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以聘請了他
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.75,0:27:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果非要說是繼承
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.44,0:27:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是圣誕繼承了我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.16,0:27:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就非要打破常規  是吧  艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.69,0:27:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是叛逆
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.16,0:27:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我覺得你說得太夸張了點
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.47,0:27:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N出自莎士比亚《奥赛罗》
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.47,0:27:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"男人應當言如其實"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.70,0:27:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"如若不然  此人定一無所是"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.81,0:27:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這樣很好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.15,0:27:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學者回歸自然
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.08,0:27:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頗有幾分"公民的不服從"之風骨
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.30,0:27:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是在暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.52,0:27:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就像現代版的梭羅  那你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.52,0:27:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N梭罗著有《论公民的不服从》  后隐居瓦尔登湖
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.09,0:27:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并無目的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.26,0:27:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是單純喜歡這種生活
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.53,0:27:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.97,0:27:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治安官從歐利希的店里搶走了我們的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.13,0:27:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.94,0:27:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老實工作  這算什么罪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.46,0:27:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他居然從餐桌上搶走了別人的晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.44,0:28:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.44,0:28:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想寫一篇社論投給報社
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.71,0:28:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別以為我不會寫
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.45,0:28:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒我打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.12,0:28:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得給報社投稿是個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.02,0:28:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯塔布斯小姐想請我們為她服務
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.66,0:28:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.83,0:28:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  艾倫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.23,0:28:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想為我的花園采集一些野花
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.57,0:28:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野花在城市的花園里能養好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.28,0:28:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要栽培方法得當
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.55,0:28:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什么不能被教養好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.65,0:28:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先把這些獵物送到德索托
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.64,0:28:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免得治安官把它們也拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.89,0:28:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午愉快  斯塔布斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.70,0:28:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.64,0:29:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見過藝術家們的描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.35,0:29:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒想到它會這么美
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.42,0:29:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同泛舟于星河之上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.29,0:29:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.03,0:29:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像星星是由糖果做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.70,0:29:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星島
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.14,0:29:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,極美星空
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.34,0:29:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.51,0:29:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,極美星空
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.24,0:29:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親在我的花園里建了一座日光浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.21,0:29:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候  不能隨意出門
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.32,0:29:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那日光浴室大得像永遠填不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.49,0:29:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我畫得滿溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.26,0:29:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等滿到沒有地方可以畫畫后
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.99,0:30:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就躺在地板中央
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.66,0:30:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在花叢之下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.77,0:30:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象我自己正在飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.50,0:30:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛毯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.77,0:30:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道瓦斯涅佐夫的畫作
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.08,0:30:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.88,0:30:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親認識俄國大使
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.88,0:30:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾繪聲繪色地描述過那幅畫的每個細節
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.09,0:30:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我感覺就像是親眼所見一般
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.06,0:30:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定認識俄國大使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.73,0:30:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親說你在俄國生活過
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.99,0:30:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次藏在花叢下的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.27,0:30:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母找不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.30,0:30:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親差點心臟病發
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.38,0:30:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要保護我的整個人生
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.97,0:30:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不受各種他所想象出的恐怖傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.68,0:30:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我卻憑空消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的避難所
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.17,0:31:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是野鳥的話  你抓不住我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.84,0:31:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認得出誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.82,0:31:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  我會是什么樣的鳥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.25,0:31:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.17,0:31:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是一只野鳥  而你在狩獵我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.40,0:31:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會是什么樣的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.73,0:31:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野鴨
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.77,0:31:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛翔時美得無與倫比
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.31,0:31:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣嗎  不過是一堆華美的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.22,0:31:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.94,0:31:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我欣賞那些鳥依靠自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.90,0:32:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慧黠躲過狩獵者
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.52,0:32:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野鴨很慧黠
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.49,0:32:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.19,0:32:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這其中是有深意的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.53,0:32:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我能否準確描述出來  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.10,0:32:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時我覺得自己就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.71,0:32:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追逐著某種
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.98,0:32:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙遠的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.52,0:32:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我射擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.42,0:32:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.86,0:32:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是打鳥  打個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.43,0:32:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的那只舊貨船  裝了東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.36,0:32:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.20,0:32:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  抓住這個  來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.84,0:33:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.08,0:33:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住槍桿
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.81,0:33:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.75,0:33:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.31,0:33:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.22,0:33:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  這是我們的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.59,0:33:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.96,0:33:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是沒被公開的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.63,0:33:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"事實坦蕩存于我的心胸之中"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.63,0:33:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N出自莎士比亚《理查二世》
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.16,0:33:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很不尋常  沃德·艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.00,0:33:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你引用名句的功力不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.97,0:33:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可不是個耐心的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.48,0:33:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能記住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.98,0:33:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.45,0:33:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能記住以后別碰我的槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.65,0:33:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.83,0:33:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.33,0:34:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.74,0:34:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決心已定了  父親
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.54,0:34:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回絕了許多大有前途的追求者  露西
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.61,0:34:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是些稚氣未脫的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.68,0:34:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對他們的父輩亦步亦趨
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.19,0:34:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在生活開始之前就知道未來了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.62,0:34:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那男人是個粗人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.22,0:34:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德·艾倫拒絕了一筆豐厚的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.46,0:34:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝知道為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.66,0:34:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要自由
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.80,0:34:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.80,0:34:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的黑奴自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.80,0:34:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.93,0:34:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西  別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.27,0:34:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們今年去避暑的時候再談這事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.44,0:34:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會陪你去葡萄園  母親
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.91,0:34:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會任由你們擺布
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.06,0:37:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德·艾倫夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.80,0:37:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的美麗驚動了夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.70,0:37:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會迅速繞地球一圈再回來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.21,0:37:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-準備好  -你敢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.58,0:37:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-別吃洋蔥和大蒜  -阻止那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.08,0:37:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們要保持氣息甜美
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.52,0:37:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會的  只要他停止開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.85,0:37:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓路
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.63,0:37:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們應該在那里等我們
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.56,0:37:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝讓我留宿  警官
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.55,0:37:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的榮幸  沃德
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.55,0:37:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望那位女士已經準備好接納你了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.14,0:37:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟女人吵架是贏不了的  你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.11,0:38:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些花招哄不好露西小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.01,0:38:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她架不住甜言蜜語  圣誕  女人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.55,0:38:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你簡直是野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.15,0:38:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.82,0:38:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.89,0:38:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西  讓我進去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.56,0:38:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以跟狗一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.99,0:38:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你該去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.00,0:38:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該跟石頭訂婚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.96,0:38:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  親愛的  至少讓我進去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.63,0:38:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我一點隱私
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.87,0:38:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱私
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.30,0:38:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得薩凡納還有人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.41,0:38:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你大半夜把我扔在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.91,0:38:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑去狂飲威士忌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.01,0:38:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  露西
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.25,0:38:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.35,0:38:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自我發泄以控制情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.76,0:38:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為我需要讓自己冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.96,0:38:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承認吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.23,0:39:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小男人勾不起你的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.77,0:39:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就這樣  愛慕著你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.38,0:39:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你表現得可真像
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.62,0:39:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.22,0:39:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.42,0:39:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N出自莎士比亚《约翰王》
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.42,0:39:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為純金鍍上金箔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.23,0:39:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替純潔的百合花涂上粉彩
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.33,0:39:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給紫羅蘭的花瓣灑上香水
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.64,0:39:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替彩虹添加一道顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.64,0:39:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在是多此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.64,0:39:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪費而可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.67,0:40:10.40,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* It's cold *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.60,0:40:13.91,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* It's cold *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.91,0:40:16.94,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Now I lost my lover *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.25,0:40:21.31,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* It's cold *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.31,0:40:23.52,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* It's cold *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.58,0:40:29.75,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* And where shall I find her? *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.46,0:40:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我來晚了  穆特里先生
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.56,0:40:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來晚好過不來  沃德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.61,0:40:47.94,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Bring me a gator *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.94,0:40:50.71,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Girl, when you get off the island *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.71,0:40:53.44,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* A ringtail 'ator *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.44,0:40:54.40,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Oh, when you get off the island *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.40,0:40:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.42,0:40:58.48,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* A Darien gator *
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.49,0:41:00.95,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Girl, when you get off the island *
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.95,0:41:05.00,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Ohh, when you get off the island *
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.00,0:41:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  就這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.16,0:41:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是全部了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.69,0:41:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐利希店要的十只  德索托要的二十只
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.44,0:41:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個捕獵季就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.84,0:41:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那見鬼的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.24,0:41:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是萊納老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.74,0:41:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說了不要進他的領地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.64,0:41:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道是我們  沃德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.25,0:41:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他知道是我們  為什么還開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.45,0:41:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他氣你跟露西小姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.66,0:41:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.99,0:41:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可幫了他大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.15,0:41:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西能把他兒子生吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.59,0:41:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他就是生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.16,0:41:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是最好的出氣筒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.99,0:41:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.53,0:41:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得離開
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.69,0:41:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊納先生  停戰
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.00,0:41:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停戰
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.70,0:41:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上  我們馬上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.90,0:41:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石頭  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.74,0:41:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  我們  我們馬上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.07,0:41:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來  上來
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.34,0:42:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.38,0:42:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來  坐下  到這來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.62,0:42:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.19,0:42:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕  從萊納開槍后你還沒說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.09,0:42:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.26,0:42:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.60,0:42:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒什么可說的  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.87,0:42:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會沒話說
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.97,0:42:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能說
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.77,0:42:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果當時只有我  情況會不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.51,0:42:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還在為那件事生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.18,0:42:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是說說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.11,0:42:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.32,0:42:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊納是想沖我開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.75,0:42:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這里的每個人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.15,0:42:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有權捍衛自己的領地
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.42,0:42:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.09,0:42:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午好  沃德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.46,0:42:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種主張是完全荒謬的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.93,0:42:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然以為如果我不在場情況會不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.37,0:42:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萊納瞄準的是我  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.81,0:43:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒打中  我們脫身了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.88,0:43:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  先生  是你脫身了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.68,0:43:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是跟著你  就像這條狗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.54,0:43:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我不在場
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.71,0:43:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會把石頭追下河殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.98,0:43:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不會  先生  他會讓你的狗活著
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.09,0:43:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是說
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.02,0:43:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的世界跟我不一樣  明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.67,0:43:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我幫忙嗎  艾倫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.41,0:43:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我一杯威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.56,0:45:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么打獵  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.99,0:45:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是紳士的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.20,0:45:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你覺得是在運動  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.60,0:45:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射殺一兩只野鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.27,0:45:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解野鳥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.94,0:45:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能分辨出灰背鴨和褐頸鴨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.58,0:45:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過它們空中轉折的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.11,0:45:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過它們獵食的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.61,0:45:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道它們經歷的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.08,0:45:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.39,0:46:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包裹在那小小胸脯里的堅定意志
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.59,0:46:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你開槍時根本毫不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.99,0:46:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.12,0:46:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽聽  一個高尚的野蠻人  
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.99,0:46:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.10,0:46:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不去想
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.83,0:46:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我獵殺二百只鴨子光明坦蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.27,0:46:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們兩個種族誕生起延續至今的交易
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.91,0:46:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.11,0:46:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你哪怕只獵殺兩只鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.18,0:46:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也叫屠殺
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.60,0:46:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槍械庫應該有槍
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.64,0:46:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家也應該有丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.00,0:47:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N约翰·艾略特·沃德  冠以胜利而背负牺牲的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.07,0:47:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰先生說你很令人擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.74,0:47:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叔叔還說什么了  穆特里先生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.88,0:47:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我圣誕就行
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.52,0:47:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.41,0:48:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰先生說他們不收夏鴨
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.31,0:48:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我不獵鴨除非太陽從西邊出來
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.15,0:48:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把我告到最高法院我也不會妥協
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.66,0:48:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"年輕人怎能為陳腐的法令所羈"
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.83,0:48:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我們不能反抗生命的本意"
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.58,0:50:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法官先生  短吻鱷獵鴨沒有限制
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.45,0:50:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浣熊獵鴨也沒有限制
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.18,0:50:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么圣誕就要有限制呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.05,0:50:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是件嚴肅的事  圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.29,0:51:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能總是判你們緩刑
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.02,0:51:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人  看守人羅西尼奧爾明確宣稱
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.11,0:51:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他于日落時分在近200米的距離外認出了我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.33,0:51:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法官大人  這是無可爭辯的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.93,0:51:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容我說一句  法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.30,0:51:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些才是無可爭辯的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.50,0:51:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近200米  日落時分
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.04,0:51:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野草這時節都長到這么高
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.64,0:51:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獵鴨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.99,0:51:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在這么深的沼澤地里
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.22,0:51:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  在近200米的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.02,0:51:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看守人羅西尼奧爾也許能辨認出
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.99,0:51:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開槍的是上帝創造出的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.66,0:51:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但絕對分不出是男是女
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.19,0:51:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更別說認出他  或她
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.83,0:51:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是縣里任何一個擁有獵槍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.17,0:51:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.30,0:51:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您還留著那把格林納爾步槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.60,0:51:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.64,0:51:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作精良啊  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.98,0:51:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.54,0:51:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果英國國王做得跟他們的槍一樣好
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.91,0:52:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱現在還是殖民地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.88,0:52:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.32,0:52:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是的  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.12,0:52:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.86,0:52:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道獵殺夏鴨違反法律嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.36,0:52:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.40,0:52:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕  那你當時為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.26,0:52:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不舍棄鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.31,0:52:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.04,0:52:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說  圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.68,0:52:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你見到看守人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.65,0:52:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么不丟掉夏鴨
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.42,0:52:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法官先生  您肯定沒吃過夏鴨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.23,0:52:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本案駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.73,0:53:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊  打開
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.49,0:53:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的槍與雄辯已無用武之地  沃德
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.49,0:53:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換種武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.38,0:55:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在建新工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.52,0:55:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.05,0:56:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝國個屁
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.66,0:56:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們只留下那一塊地
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.26,0:56:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板的新獵場
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.53,0:56:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傻瓜也不想想
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.50,0:56:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這兒到大沼澤地有那么多低地
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.91,0:56:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鴨子干嘛偏要往那塊混凝土飛
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.08,0:56:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兒沒法打獵了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.45,0:56:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.75,0:56:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.42,0:56:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最后一次見到他
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.06,0:56:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在那棵樹邊上
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.98,0:57:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.68,0:57:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石頭總是盡職盡責
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.98,0:57:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今它完成了最后的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.52,0:57:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎士比亞都不可能說得比你好  圣誕
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.99,0:58:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"獵鴨人如何避免成為罪犯"
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.78,0:58:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有沒有告訴你我找到
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.51,0:58:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德在報紙上發表的一些文章
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.58,0:58:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽聽這個
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.12,0:58:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,題目叫"獵鴨人如何避免成為罪犯"
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.22,0:58:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"隨著各種有關獵鴨的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.06,0:58:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不合理的荒謬法令出臺
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.79,0:58:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們要在短暫的漁獵期獵鴨
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.96,0:58:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會違反那些愚蠢的禁止條令
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.63,0:59:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要避免成為罪犯  最安全的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.54,0:59:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是當他去獵鴨時
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.84,0:59:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不開一槍"
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.84,0:59:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德很高產
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.99,0:59:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用露西送他的鋼筆阻擋時代的洪流
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.59,0:59:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  努力阻擋
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.79,0:59:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都騰空了閣樓
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.76,0:59:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用來給萊拉開歷史學會
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.92,0:59:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍默用二百個板條箱給她建了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.29,0:59:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒收一分錢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.03,0:59:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍默他爸也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.03,0:59:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用幾把舊槍抵消了沃德的賬務
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.60,0:59:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸參加搜救隊找到了沃德的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.94,0:59:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說發現他時  他正穿著睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.38,0:59:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人說那不是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.25,0:59:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.88,0:59:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.62,0:59:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管沃德在尋找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.16,1:00:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已離他遠去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.83,1:00:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如把那幅也拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.04,1:00:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕  我
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.18,1:00:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你找了個住處
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.25,1:00:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒適
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.18,1:00:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是家  但我盡力安排了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.35,1:00:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住在那兒會很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.40,1:00:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.23,1:00:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你說什么來著  圣誕
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.77,1:00:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走以后別犯懶
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.74,1:00:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓火熄滅
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.31,1:00:55.98,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Jack t' the rack back, stickit ball a hack *
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.98,1:00:59.12,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Low ball high ball, scallion Jack *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.09,1:01:03.55,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Jack t' the rack back, stickit ball a hack *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.56,1:01:05.39,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Low ball high ball, scallion Jack *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.39,1:01:07.82,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Jack t' the rack back, stickit ball a hack *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.83,1:01:09.73,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Low ball high ball, scallion Jack *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.73,1:01:11.09,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Jack t' the rack back, stickit ball a hack *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.10,1:01:13.00,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Low ball high ball, scallion Jack *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.00,1:01:14.50,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Jack t' the rack back, stickit ball a hack *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.50,1:01:16.07,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Low ball high ball, scallion Jack *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.07,1:01:17.60,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Jack t' the rack back, stickit ball a hack *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.60,1:01:18.67,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Low ball high ball, scallion... *
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.47,1:01:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就像個獵人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.44,1:01:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一槍驚飛了兩群鳥
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.61,1:02:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我問你們  我該朝哪邊射擊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.92,1:02:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正別射你同行的獵人  看在上帝的份上
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.89,1:02:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什么
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.53,1:02:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什么
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.10,1:02:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該瞄準制定這條可惡法律的城里人嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.97,1:02:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只會虛張聲勢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.11,1:02:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故作姿態
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.01,1:02:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那玩意兒有著鴨的腳
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.01,1:02:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇的心  驢的蠢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.65,1:02:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.45,1:02:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們這些鄉下人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.22,1:02:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未能盡責使用自己的槍
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.33,1:02:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才使得城里人制定了這條可怕的法律
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.31,1:03:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呦喂
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.35,1:03:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  露西小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.65,1:03:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你認為你在逃避什么
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.89,1:03:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有逃避
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.83,1:03:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道在哪兒能找到我
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.83,1:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說你在逃避我
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.50,1:03:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.37,1:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解你  沃德·艾倫
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.13,1:03:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的能力
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.84,1:03:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出你現在離目標有多遠
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.60,1:03:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親愛的  你在質疑我的槍法嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.04,1:03:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在質疑你的選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.11,1:03:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是那些會讓你英年早逝的選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.78,1:03:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人  你當我是你的哈巴狗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.38,1:03:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在你的腳邊  唯命是從
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.92,1:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴你  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.32,1:03:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連獵犬也有自己的本能
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.59,1:03:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按自己的意愿行動
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.16,1:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要它是只稱職的獵犬
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.69,1:03:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你自己比成狗還真是恰當
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.10,1:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汪  我是自己的主宰
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.63,1:04:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管我  女人
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.77,1:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.34,1:04:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說話你就得聽
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.07,1:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要開槍打我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.12,1:04:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還了解我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.19,1:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按原告所述
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.92,1:04:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事發當日
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.79,1:04:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據其親眼所見
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.60,1:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她聲稱是我
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.40,1:04:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準確無誤地射穿了這幅畫像的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.87,1:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在距離
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.31,1:04:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十五步之遠
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.91,1:04:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的客廳是屋子里最大的房間
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.05,1:04:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,測試一個人是否清醒有很多方法
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.49,1:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我告訴各位  這樣的槍法
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.62,1:05:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是測試方法之一
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.83,1:05:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由此只能推斷出
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.33,1:05:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位尊敬的夫人所做的陳述
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.73,1:05:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自相矛盾
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.63,1:05:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么是我醉了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.34,1:05:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么是我開的槍
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.51,1:05:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是毋庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.01,1:05:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毋庸置疑  這兩種陳述
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.68,1:05:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相矛盾
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.75,1:05:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒謬了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.39,1:05:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫先生  你作為一名神槍手聲名在外
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.43,1:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯然  我無須枉法或誤判
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.96,1:05:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以直接駁回指控  放你走人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.33,1:05:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,華麗的邏輯并不能改變事實
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.10,1:05:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐  艾倫夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.44,1:05:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.07,1:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我發現為了公眾安全的利益
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.98,1:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須判你有罪
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.38,1:05:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.78,1:05:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判你入獄十天
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.85,1:05:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽啊  聽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.98,1:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肅靜  肅靜
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.08,1:05:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-這是暴行  -上前來
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.48,1:05:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就上前
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.95,1:06:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十天估計還不夠平息她的怒火
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.32,1:06:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是你  我會把這十天用來
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.69,1:06:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用文字構建一個王國
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.33,1:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈禱自己得到救贖
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.80,1:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  沃德·艾倫  錯了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.51,1:07:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  沃德·艾倫  也許錯了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.48,1:07:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你去查看
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.52,1:07:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽有沒有從西邊出來之前
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.85,1:07:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想強調  我將會
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.32,1:07:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是說我已經
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.52,1:07:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會對我的生活做任何改變
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.96,1:07:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但似乎我們的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.66,1:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了分岔路口
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.86,1:07:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界選擇了一條路
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.23,1:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我選了另一條
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.94,1:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許這個結果無法避免
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.04,1:08:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們每個人都注定會發覺
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.91,1:08:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來  都是一個人獨行
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.81,1:08:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是那些認為世界
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.02,1:08:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近乎完美的人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.35,1:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些接受世事起伏的人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.33,1:08:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一條河流
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.16,1:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里  歲月是生命的終極塑造者
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.26,1:08:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里  繁衍  遷徙  甚至是死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.80,1:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆由著上帝的意愿
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.88,1:08:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著歷史的車輪滾滾前行
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.97,1:08:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一些人卻決意要
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.27,1:08:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重造車輪  逆流而上
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.85,1:08:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們似乎已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.68,1:08:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許他們是對的  他們也這么做了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.22,1:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口涌起的沖動
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.25,1:08:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驅動著人類無止境工業化的腳步
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.16,1:08:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我們的存在是為了再造一切
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.79,1:08:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重塑一切
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.93,1:08:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創造我們自己對于完美的新理念
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.70,1:09:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把上帝的旨意留在歷史的陰影之中
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.40,1:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我  一直在與新理念作斗爭
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.74,1:09:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕那理念
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.88,1:09:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得那理念可憎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.55,1:09:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我錯了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.68,1:09:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我并不這么認為
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.85,1:09:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我相信  如果人類整體取得了進步
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.05,1:09:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為承受了野性的洗禮
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.49,1:09:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們將野性重塑成溫和
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.56,1:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們將走向衰落
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.07,1:09:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我所做的一切換來的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.97,1:09:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是雙傷痕累累的拳頭
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.37,1:09:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷害了我和我的愛人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.51,1:09:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而非我的本意目標
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.78,1:09:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  也許我應該
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.41,1:09:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉆研那些書卷
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.38,1:09:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且聽從莎翁的指引
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.65,1:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"讓你的墨水里摻滿怨毒"
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.65,1:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N出自莎士比亚《第十二夜》
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.22,1:10:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得一試
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.09,1:10:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N萨凡纳市立监狱
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.67,1:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  讀了我的文章嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.44,1:10:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.74,1:10:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.91,1:10:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.02,1:10:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再受屈了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.93,1:10:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為一個母親那樣不合適
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.96,1:10:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布萊森醫生已經確定了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.47,1:10:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.33,1:10:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別急著說話  沃德
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.14,1:10:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你仔仔細細地想想你現在的感受
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.11,1:10:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我可不能忍受
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.14,1:10:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我說謊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.53,1:11:11.36,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Oh, bring me a gator *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.36,1:11:14.03,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Girl, when you come off the island *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.03,1:11:16.07,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Whoa, just a ringtail 'ator *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.44,1:11:20.27,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Girl, when you come off the island *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.27,1:11:23.27,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Just a Darien gator *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.28,1:11:25.81,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Girl, when you come off the island *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.81,1:11:29.21,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Oh, girl, when you come off the island *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.21,1:11:31.55,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Oh, girl, when you come off the island *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.55,1:11:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配額就這些了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.49,1:11:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐利希店要的十二只
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.09,1:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德索托要的二十只
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.56,1:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后  他們會把這些野鴨子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.73,1:11:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過雜貨店再賣給我們
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.26,1:11:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且價格是我們賣給他們的兩倍
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.97,1:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.74,1:11:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看那個
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.57,1:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西那天看到的船
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.61,1:12:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西打中了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.22,1:12:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.15,1:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是這艘船最傳奇的故事了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.02,1:12:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這船還能航行嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.59,1:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說漂浮  那應該可以
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.23,1:12:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕  白櫟木
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.17,1:12:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗吉尼亞的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.09,1:12:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候約翰叔叔帶我去過里士滿
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.09,1:12:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N美国内战时南方联邦的首都
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.45,1:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我戰爭快爆發了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.05,1:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你講過我的樹屋嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.22,1:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰叔叔建的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.62,1:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝爾曼開近的時候爬上艾倫樹屋
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.62,1:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N美国内战将军  以焦土政策闻名
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.86,1:12:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嚇得半死
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.99,1:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說如果北方佬把大房子都燒了  我們就住在這里
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.31,1:13:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你目睹過內戰吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.91,1:13:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  先生
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.00,1:13:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太小了  不記得
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.56,1:13:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.09,1:13:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不讓人老實工作了  還能干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.10,1:13:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要賣掉這些鴨子  至少還得等兩小時呢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.34,1:14:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你個驚喜
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.77,1:14:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德  別這樣偷偷接近我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.41,1:14:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你想把孩子現在就給嚇出來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.28,1:14:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給兒子
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.35,1:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是女兒呢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.89,1:14:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都一樣  我只想給你看看
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.71,1:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來一個你打獵時的表情  沃德
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.95,1:14:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.21,1:14:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他看看你打獵時的表情
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.12,1:14:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治安官  我可一只也沒有多打
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.69,1:15:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德  是你的夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.79,1:15:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有兒子啦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.79,1:15:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  沃德
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.02,1:15:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.26,1:15:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她正在休息  -我就陪她坐坐
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.86,1:15:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不行  沃德
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.36,1:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我兒子在哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.22,1:18:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德  你不能
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.89,1:18:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一味排斥"精神收容所"
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.76,1:18:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是很好的庇護所
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.60,1:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有別的辦法
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.20,1:18:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她需要不間斷的照料
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.87,1:18:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必要時得強制喂食和洗澡
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.48,1:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.71,1:18:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他連不讓她在外面淋雨都做不到
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.72,1:18:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許她會好起來的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.56,1:19:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需在這里簽個字
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.40,1:19:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有筆
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.14,1:19:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶你看樣東西
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.73,1:21:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出身于聲名顯赫的家族
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.00,1:21:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了自己的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.01,1:22:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己也說過
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.78,1:22:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太浮夸
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.35,1:22:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.29,1:22:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真實的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.53,1:22:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條河流  還有你
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.91,1:22:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就該帶你來這里
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.94,1:23:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好冷
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.74,1:25:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你超出配額了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.47,1:25:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.11,1:25:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說好是長期訂單的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.95,1:25:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漁獵委員會來過了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.45,1:25:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們告訴我如果我再從你這兒進貨
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.18,1:25:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就吊銷我的營業證
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.78,1:25:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得哈登法官希望
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.35,1:25:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天的早餐盤中空空是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.92,1:25:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點骨氣吧  馬賽厄斯
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.09,1:25:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瘋了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.53,1:25:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瘋了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.00,1:25:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想見識什么叫瘋嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.06,1:25:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓你見識見識
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.47,1:25:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.94,1:25:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.01,1:25:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里不再是我們的地方了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.65,1:27:13.52,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* If you see my mother *
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.09,1:27:19.16,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Oh, yes *
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.50,1:27:27.10,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Won't you tell her from me *
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.27,1:27:30.84,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Oh, yes *
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.14,1:27:36.81,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* I'm a-riding my horse *
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.81,1:27:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起來
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.98,1:27:39.72,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* In the battlefield *
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.95,1:27:50.49,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* I want to see my Jesus in the morning *
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.20,1:28:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大火后那家人回來過沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.42,1:28:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你熟悉周邊水域嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.16,1:28:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些錢夠讓你幫我了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.80,1:28:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一個河上向導
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.74,1:28:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫先生什么東西都不要了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.41,1:28:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要了  沃爾頓先生
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.88,1:28:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把房子賣掉
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.08,1:28:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給露西女士提供最好的條件
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.96,1:28:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃爾頓先生
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.10,1:29:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許還有件東西
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.01,1:29:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按你所說辦了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.85,1:29:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西女士會過上舒適的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.38,1:29:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃爾頓先生會安排好的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.49,1:29:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈登法官讓我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.00,1:29:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們維護現存法律
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.00,1:30:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市級法院不能與聯邦作對
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.16,1:30:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報紙上都登了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.66,1:30:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈登法官把他的舊船借給你了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.00,1:30:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你留著
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.93,1:30:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你保證
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.74,1:30:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時不時在星期天給他送只鴨子去
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.68,1:30:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍默先生說會把你的郵件寄到五金商店
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.96,1:30:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會到霍默那里取你的郵件的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.54,1:30:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  沃德先生
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.80,1:31:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克  我得確認下
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.77,1:31:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把圣誕趕出去
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.14,1:31:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅伊  我一直在考慮這事
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.11,1:31:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕已經95歲了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.00,1:32:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能會活到105歲
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.31,1:32:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在圣誕節那天出生于[佛州]馬爾伯里
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.98,1:32:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是那個莊園最后的幸存者了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.28,1:32:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是家人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.09,1:32:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是血親
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.29,1:32:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但被釋黑奴是有權利的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.72,1:32:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰·艾略特·沃德親自立下的契約
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.36,1:32:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是關鍵  杰克
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.93,1:32:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  圣誕都照顧不了自己
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.43,1:32:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不給他送吃的  他可能都餓死了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.14,1:32:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為你會把這酒留到特別的時刻
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.77,1:32:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有比現在更特別的時刻了  羅伊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.65,1:32:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來問問你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.09,1:32:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有停下來仔細聽過以前黑奴唱的歌
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.59,1:32:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們唱的我一句都聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.06,1:32:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唱首給你聽
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.93,1:33:00.10,Lyric2,NTP,0,0,0,,我要坐在那簡陋的搖椅上
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.10,1:33:04.51,Lyric2,NTP,0,0,0,,我要慢慢地搖來搖去
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.51,1:33:08.01,Lyric2,NTP,0,0,0,,我要慢慢地搖來搖去
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.01,1:33:10.18,Lyric2,NTP,0,0,0,,直到死去
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.18,1:33:13.48,Lyric2,NTP,0,0,0,,直到死去
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.48,1:33:16.59,Lyric2,NTP,0,0,0,,直到死去
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.59,1:33:20.02,Lyric2,NTP,0,0,0,,我要坐在那簡陋的搖椅上
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.02,1:33:22.12,Lyric2,NTP,0,0,0,,直到死去
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.66,1:33:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個好人  杰克
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.53,1:33:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但記住我的話
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.10,1:33:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的正是
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.87,1:33:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你無法阻擋時間
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.95,1:33:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用露西送他的鋼筆阻擋時代的洪流
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.95,1:35:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的槍與雄辯已無用武之地  沃德
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.09,1:35:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換種武器吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.20,1:35:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我寫過幾十篇關于狩獵的文章
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.44,1:35:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有超過兩倍的抨擊愚蠢狩獵法令的文章
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.71,1:35:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概比任何人都懂如何引經據典
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.71,1:35:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用扯牛津那套
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.45,1:35:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以說出
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.33,1:35:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數十種羽毛的名字  顏色  用途與用法
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.02,1:35:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少數十種水鳥的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.63,1:35:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己收集了很多南方聯邦的錢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.57,1:35:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從戰爭結束前就開始攢了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.87,1:35:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有積攢了一輩子的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.33,1:35:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在當今世上幾乎毫無用處的實踐經驗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.41,1:36:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我深愛的河流上度過了十五年光陰
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.65,1:36:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那該死的一切將我沖上了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.48,1:36:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也辨認不出的城市岸邊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.38,1:36:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里住滿了我未曾邀請的人們
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.62,1:36:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了那么多次
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.79,1:36:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果現在看來我贏錯了地方
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.60,1:36:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.67,1:36:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里是我曾泛舟的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.40,1:37:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕  你懶到都不偶爾捅一捅火了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.31,1:37:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你帶了塊巴布斯核桃派
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.61,1:37:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰尼硬要她做一個帶去學校
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.44,1:37:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說除非分圣誕一片才行
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.55,1:37:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.09,1:37:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讀了沃德在報紙上的最后一篇文章
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.49,1:37:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.80,1:38:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰克
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.80,1:38:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德·艾倫在理發椅上睡著了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.81,1:38:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在那之前  他立下了規矩
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.65,1:38:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說  絕對不能
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.55,1:38:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動他的胡子
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.77,1:38:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"俄國大使對沃德·艾倫說
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.95,1:38:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是再敢回俄國
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.22,1:38:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會親自把你押到沙皇面前
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.00,1:38:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐐銬加身"
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.39,1:38:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"圣誕·穆特里比世上
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.20,1:39:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一個人都更了解沃德·艾倫
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.93,1:39:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一個生來是莊園主
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.67,1:39:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而另一個是奴隸出身
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.10,1:39:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們卻成了性情相投的摯友
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.99,1:39:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小  我就和圣誕一起打獵
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.08,1:39:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河面上忙碌了一天后
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.38,1:39:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕會坐在壁爐前的搖椅上
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.68,1:39:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凝視著沃德的照片
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.18,1:39:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地  細細地
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.19,1:39:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,講他的白人朋友"
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.09,1:39:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕講了一個故事
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.22,1:39:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都一模一樣的故事
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.60,1:39:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字字不差
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.04,1:39:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一個故事他從來都沒有講給我聽過
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.87,1:39:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我問了他幾百次
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.64,1:39:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德·艾倫是怎么死的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.65,1:39:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為他是想自己默默悼念
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.75,1:39:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我沒意識到
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.92,1:40:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這一生中他都在告訴我這個故事
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.79,1:40:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.23,1:40:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他一直撐著活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.87,1:40:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了等我明白
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.60,1:40:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.34,1:40:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  兒子
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.91,1:40:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.52,1:41:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就該帶你來這里
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.03,1:41:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.03,1:41:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我拿到了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.97,1:41:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.47,1:41:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他像野牛比爾
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.04,1:41:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  很像
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.54,1:41:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德是薩凡納河上最好的獵手
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.51,1:41:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有沒有跟你說過
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.34,1:41:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有次射穿了露西畫像上的雙眼
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.58,1:41:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干凈利落  就射穿了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.00,1:41:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.72,1:41:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  在那里
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.99,1:41:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看見沒
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.79,1:41:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是鶴嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.26,1:41:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  你覺得沃德·艾倫是怎么死的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.43,1:41:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兒子  一個人的死之所以重要
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.47,1:41:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是看如何反映了他的一生
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.21,1:42:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是他自己活過的日子
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.95,1:42:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是有更深層的意義
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.42,1:42:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這其中是有深意的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.42,1:42:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得自己就在那里
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.29,1:42:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追逐而去
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.13,1:42:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追逐著某種
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.07,1:42:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙遠的目標
